{"tid":1518664,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打絲打可以救下我隻狗","createTime":"2019-08-30T10:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T10:49:38.000Z","uid":24162,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f7020bfa21148d2ff607842116d71524c66eccef","tid":1518664,"uid":24162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"一隻唐狗急需狗狗輸血續命 HCT 9.2% 情況好危急！！！<br />\n狗狗名稱：花鼠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歲數：6歲<br />\n血型：1.1-<br />\n體重：14.9kg（中型狗）<br />\n----------------------------------------------------<br />\n要求狗狗<br />\n血型 : 1.1-<br />\n體重： 體重25kg以上即可<br />\n*需健康有打開防疫針冇長期病患冇牛蜱熱和心絲蟲抗體<br />\n捐血量：300mL or more<br />\n診所：錦田動物醫院<br />\n聯絡方法： <a href=\"https://t.me/plshelpmydog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fplshelpmydog&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=626f6528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/plshelpmydog</a><br />\n<br />\n醫生話只需簡單驗血配對及輸血，不需留院，即日可完成，費用全由我們付<br />\n<br />\n我們已曾找到兩位有心人的狗狗幫忙，可惜最後血液不融。。<br />\n希望有好心人好心狗可以幫助花鼠渡過難關，花鼠的紅血球和血小板都嚴重不足，不知道還可以撐多久<br />\n<br />\n萬分感謝大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb1c787efa8fb78fb22715eddaac323831a4634","tid":1518664,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUQvG7y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUQvG7y.gif&h=0b84475f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=92145d70\" target=\"_blank